{{update|date=October 2018}} {{Infobox sailing competition | year = 2018 | type =Extreme Sailing Series | image = | alt = | caption = | edition = 12th | dates = 14 March – 2 December | key_people = | titles = | competitors = | yachts = [[GC32]] | nations = | winner = | award1_title = | award1 = | prev = [[2017 Extreme Sailing Series|2017]] | next = ''[[2019 Extreme Sailing Series|2019]]'' }}
The '''2018 [[Extreme Sailing Series]]''' is a series of [[GC32]] [[catamaran]] class [[Sailing (sport)|sailing]] events scheduled to be staged during 2018. The series began in March in [[Muscat]], [[Oman]], and the final event is due to take place in [[Los Cabos]], [[Mexico]] in late November.<ref>{{cite web|title=Extreme Sailing Series™ confirms eight-stop global tour in 2018|url=https://www.extremesailingseries.com/news/view/extreme-sailing-series-confirms-eight-stop-global-tour-in-2018|website=Extreme Sailing Series|accessdate=15 March 2018}}</ref>
==Events==
