The 2018 series will consist of eight acts across three continents, and will include the inaugural G32 World Championship in [[Riva del Garda]], [[Italy]].<ref>{{cite web|title=2018 Extreme Sailing Series™ Events|url=https://www.extremesailingseries.com/events/2018|website=Extreme Sailing Series|accessdate=15 March 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=First GC32 World Championship will be held on Lake Garda|url=http://www.sailing.org/news/85786.php#.WqrxEGacawU|website=World Sailing|accessdate=15 March 2018}}</ref>
