| tenants     = [[Saraperos de Saltillo]]<ref name="world_stadia">The stadium is listed as ''Parque Francisco I. Madero'' (distinct from the smaller [[association football]] stadium in Saltillo with a similar name) at: {{Cite web|url=http://www.worldstadiums.com/north_america/countries/mexico/northern_mexico.shtml|title=World Stadiums - Stadiums in Mexico :: Northern Mexico|accessdate=2011-06-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605142819/http://www.worldstadiums.com/north_america/countries/mexico/northern_mexico.shtml|archivedate=2011-06-05|df=}}</ref>
