'''Nadine Joy Nathan''' (born {{birth date|1999|12|29|df=yes}}) is a Singaporean female [[artistic gymnast]], representing her nation at international competitions. 

She competed at world championships, including the [[2014 Youth Olympic Games]], and the [[2015 World Artistic Gymnastics Championships]] in Glasgow.<ref>{{cite web|title=2015 World Gymnastics Championships athletes - Nadine Joy Nathan|url=http://gym.longinestiming.com/File/00000E00010001FFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF00 |work=longinestiming.com|date= |accessdate=27 January 2016}}</ref>

