[[Image:Logo of the SCF.jpg|thumb|SCF logo]]
The '''Swedish Cycling Federation'''  or '''SCF''' (in [[Swedish language|Swedish]]: ''Svenska Cykelförbundet'') was established in 1900, and is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Sweden]].

The SCF is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Union Européenne de Cyclisme|UEC]].

